facilities unveils a dazzling display of storage batteries, tiny
and large that range from self-charging units you can use marooned
in the jungle or powerful units that can run a notebook computer
for 11 hours straight. The metro Atlanta research and battery
production line are the flagship of Motorola's worldwide batter
production subsidiary. (Holsendolph, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
