<P>
   Turkey is making itself more ``user-friendly'' to Americans with
the establishment of a toll-free line for information _ 877-FOR
TURKEY _ and a new Web site dedicated to tourism _ www.
</P>
<P>
   tourismturkey.org. The site includes hundreds of pages of
information to assist travelers in planning a trip.
</P>
