attorneys general must agree on what penalties to recommend to U.S.
District Judge Thomas Penfield Jackson, and Microsoft officials
must overcome what some call the take-no-prisoners ``Gates
culture'' to fashion a new settlement proposal more acceptable to
the government. (Glass, Cox News Service). 22.
