<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-04 18:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6961 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w BC-MICROSOFT05-COX     04-04 0662
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MICROSOFT05-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    LARGE ISSUES STILL LOOM FOR MICROSOFT AND GOVERNMENT
 &HT;    With MICROSOFT-CONGRESS. Moving in Washington (w) and financial
(f) categories.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
